# Matrimonial Project Reorganization вЂ” Role-Based Architecture

Reorganize the existing React Matrimonial project into a clean, scalable, role-based architecture with protected routing, separate layouts, and professional folder structure вЂ” **without breaking existing UI or functionality**.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **File move strategy:** All files will be moved to new locations with updated imports. The old `src/admin/` and `src/user/` directories will be removed after migration. Existing component internals remain untouched.

> [!WARNING]
> **The existing `AuthContext.jsx` will be enhanced** with a `role` field (`"admin"` or `"user"`) and login/register functions will set the role. The current `user` object from `storage.js` will be extended вЂ” no data loss.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Route URL changes:** User dashboard pages currently at `/afterlogin/dashboard`, `/afterlogin/profile`, etc. will move to `/user/dashboard`, `/user/profile`, etc. Admin routes remain at `/admin/*`. Public pages stay at `/`, `/login`, `/register`, etc.

---

