---

### Routes

#### [NEW] [ProtectedRoute.jsx](file:///d:/Project_new/React/Matrimonial/src/routes/ProtectedRoute.jsx)

Reusable wrapper that:
- Checks if `user` exists in `AuthContext` в†’ if not, redirects to `/login`
- Checks `user.role` against an `allowedRoles` prop в†’ if wrong role, redirects to `/unauthorized`
- Renders `<Outlet />` if authorized

#### [NEW] [AdminRoutes.jsx](file:///d:/Project_new/React/Matrimonial/src/routes/AdminRoutes.jsx)

Defines all `/admin/*` routes wrapped in `ProtectedRoute` with `allowedRoles={["admin"]}` and `AdminLayout`.

#### [NEW] [UserRoutes.jsx](file:///d:/Project_new/React/Matrimonial/src/routes/UserRoutes.jsx)

Defines all `/user/*` routes wrapped in `ProtectedRoute` with `allowedRoles={["user"]}` and `UserDashboardLayout`.

#### [NEW] [PublicRoutes.jsx](file:///d:/Project_new/React/Matrimonial/src/routes/PublicRoutes.jsx)

Defines public routes (`/`, `/login`, `/register`, `/packages`, etc.) with `UserPublicLayout`.

---

### Layouts

#### [NEW] [AdminLayout.jsx](file:///d:/Project_new/React/Matrimonial/src/layouts/AdminLayout.jsx)

Extracted from `Admin.jsx`: renders admin `Navbar` + `Sidebar` + `<Outlet />`. No route definitions inside.

#### [NEW] [UserPublicLayout.jsx](file:///d:/Project_new/React/Matrimonial/src/layouts/UserPublicLayout.jsx)

Extracted from `App.jsx` `UserLayout`: renders public `Navbar` + `Preloader` logic + `<Outlet />`.

#### [NEW] [UserDashboardLayout.jsx](file:///d:/Project_new/React/Matrimonial/src/layouts/UserDashboardLayout.jsx)

Renamed/moved from `MainLayout.jsx`: renders user dashboard `Navbar` + `Sidebar` + `<Outlet />`.

---

### Context

#### [MODIFY] [AuthContext.jsx](file:///d:/Project_new/React/Matrimonial/src/context/AuthContext.jsx)

- Add `role` field to user object (read from stored user data)
- Add `login(userData)` function that sets user with role
- Ensure backward compatibility with existing `loadData()` logic

